sentences.english: As a result many of the females can't breed, and fewer chicks are produced.
sentences.chinese: 其結果是很多雌鳥無法繁殖，新生幼雛較少。

sentences.english: The day-old chicks were then taken to the holding facility in a four-wheel-drive.
sentences.chinese: 才一天大的幼雛被帶到了四輪車上的設備裏。

sentences.english: The most ferocious creatures are disarmed by caresses bestowed on their young.
sentences.chinese: 最兇猛的禽獸，見人家撫摸它的幼雛也會馴服起來的。
